SUMMARY:Cape May Harbor Beach Sweep
DESCRIPTION:Clean Ocean Action and the Nature Center of Cape May are collaborating to help clean our ocean and harbor beaches in Cape May. Join us! Join us at the Nature Center to help clean our ocean and harbor beaches here in Cape May. This date coincides with Clean Ocean Action’s annual Beach Sweeps. This is a great community service project for your civic organization or scout group. Additionally\, we’ll plant\, mulch\, deadhead\, weed\, and prune throughout the Center’s grounds and along the harbor! Pre-registration is not required but allows you to receive updates about this event. \n\n\n\nCOST: FREE \n\n\nCANCELLATION POLICY: NJ Audubon’s programs require a minimum number of registrants to run. If we cancel\, due to lack of participation\, severe weather\, or unforeseen circumstances\, all participants will be notified as soon as possible and are eligible for a full refund. Participants may cancel without penalty if greater than 48 hours in advance. Sorry\, no refund for cancellations less than 48 hours in advance unless due to health emergencies; however\, registrations can be transferred to another program in the future. \nREGISTER HERE
URL:https://njaudubon.org/event/cape-may-harbor-beach-sweep-3/
